1_faq_sections_0_faq_questions_and_answers_0_faq_question','What is a bridging loan?'),(1387,116,'_flexible_1_faq_sections_0_faq_questions_and_answers_0_faq_question','field_6251d4b125b66'),(1388,116,'flexible_1_faq_sections_0_faq_questions_and_answers_0_faq_answer','A bridging loan is a short-term loan (usually up to 12 months) that can be secured against a property and is designed to ‘bridge the gap’ until longer-term finance can be arranged, or an underlying security is realised.'),(1389,116,'_flexible_1_faq_sections_0_faq_questions_and_answers_0_faq_answer','field_6251d4bb25b67'),(1390,116,'flexible_1_faq_sections_0_faq_questions_and_answers_1_faq_question','What can a bridging loan be used for?'),(1391,116,'_flexible_1_faq_sections_0_faq_questions_and_answers_1_faq_question','field_6251d4b125b66'),(1392,116,'flexible_1_faq_sections_0_faq_questions_and_answers_1_faq_answer','A bridging loan can be used to complete on a property or auction purchase, to bridge the gap between buying a property and securing a mortgage, or if you want to develop or refurbish a property project. See <a href=\"http://localhost/inflow/products/\">our products</a> for more details.'),(1393,116,'_flexible_1_faq_sections_0_faq_questions_and_answers_1_faq_answer','field_6251d4bb25b67'),(1394,116,'flexible_1_faq_sections_0_faq_questions_and_answers_2_faq_question','Why use a bridging loan?'),(1395,116,'_flexible_1_faq_sections_0_faq_questions_and_answers_2_faq_question','field_6251d4b125b66'),(1396,116,'flexible_1_faq_sections_0_faq_questions_and_answers_2_faq_answer','Bridging loans have inherently flexible features which can make them an attractive alternative to mainstream lending. One of the most favourable aspects of a bridging loan is the speed in which it can be arranged.\r\n\r\nYou can use bridging loans for:\r\n- Maintaining a place in a sale chain\r\n- Unmortgageable properties e.g. no kitchen and bathroom.\r\n- Dilapidated properties\r\n- First time Investor and Developer considered\r\nBuying a Property at Auction\r\n- For quick purchases when a bargain property deal comes along\r\n- Buying a property with a short lease &amp; Lease extension funding\r\n- Ground up Development\r\n- Refurbishment Properties\r\n- Lend against the market value as opposed to the purchase price\r\n- Cross Collateralisation – Able to use more than one security address to achieving 100% lending\r\n- 2nd Charge lending\r\n- No minimum Income required\r\n- Adverse Credit considered\r\n- Rescue &amp; Recovery Deals\r\n- Cash Buyer Only properties\r\n- Freehold Flats\r\n- Semi Commercial or Commercial Properties including Vacant shops\r\n- 100% Refurbishment Finance\r\n- Planning Gain Opportunities\r\n- Airspace Development'),(1397,116,'_flexible_1_faq_sections_0_faq_questions_and_answers_2_faq_answer','field_6251d4bb25b67'),(1398,116,'flexible_1_faq_sections_0_faq_questions_and_answers_3_faq_question','What is the criteria for a bridging loan?'),(1399,116,'_flexible_1_faq_sections_0_faq_questions_and_answers_3_faq_question','field_6251d4b125b66'),(1400,116,'flexible_1_faq_sections_0_faq_questions_and_answers_3_faq_answer','Inflow understands there is no ‘one size fits all’ criteria when it comes to a bridging loan. We apply a combination of technology and manual underwriting to ensure the full understanding of your circumstances enabling us to provide fast, flexible property finance.'),(1401,116,'_flexible_1_faq_sections_0_faq_questions_and_answers_3_faq_answer','field_6251d4bb25b67'),(1402,116,'flexible_1_faq_sections_0_faq_questions_and_answers_4_faq_question','How quickly could I borrow?'),(1403,116,'_flexible_1_faq_sections_0_faq_questions_and_answers_4_faq_question','field_6251d4b125b66'),(1404,116,'flexible_1_faq_sections_0_faq_questions_and_answers_4_faq_answer','At Inflow, our processes are designed to make obtaining property finance simple. Terms can be agreed within hours with funds released typically in 15-20 days or much quicker if the circumstances require.'),(1405,116,'_flexible_1_faq_sections_0_faq_questions_and_answers_4_faq_answer','field_6251d4bb25b67'),(1406,116,'flexible_1_faq_sections_0_faq_questions_and_answers','25'),(1407,116,'_flexible_1_faq_sections_0_faq_questions_and_answers','field_6251d49625b65'),(1408,116,'flexible_1_faq_sections','1'),(1409,116,'_flexible_1_faq_sections','field_6251d43b25b63'),(1410,116,'flexible_1_active','1'),(1411,116,'_flexible_1_active','field_6251a4d4d7bab'),(1412,208,'flexible_0_section_background_image','188'),(1413,208,'_flexible_0_section_background_image','field_6251ceb34e168'),(1414,208,'flexible_0_main_title','Frequently Asked Questions'),(1415,208,'_flexible_0_main_title','field_6251ceb34e167'),(1416,208,'flexible_0_section_short_description','How is it to get a loan with Inflow'),(1417,208,'_flexible_0_section_short_description','field_6251ceb34e169'),(1418,208,'flexible_0_button_option',''),(1419,208,'_flexible_0_button_option','field_6251ceb34e16b'),(1420,208,'flexible_0_active','1'),(1421,208,'_flexible_0_active','field_6251ceb34e16d'),(1422,208,'flexible','a:2:{i:0;s:20:\"hero_section_smaller\";i:1;s:11:\"faq_section\";}'),(1423,208,'_flexible','field_624f096c944c5'),(1424,208,'flexible_0_section_background_color',''),(1425,208,'_flexible_0_section_background_color','field_6251cf470bb06'),(1426,208,'flexible_1_section_main_title','Borrowers'),(1427,208,'_flexible_1_section_main_title','field_6251a4d4d7ba8'),(1428,208,'flexible_1_faq_sections_0_faq_sections_titles','About Inflow'),(1429,208,'_flexible_1_faq_sections_0_faq_sections_titles','field_6251d48325b64'),(1430,208,'flexible_1_faq_sections_0_faq_questions_and_answers_0_faq_question','How much can I borrow?'),(1431,208,'_flexible_1_faq_sections_0_faq_questions_and_answers_0_faq_question','field_6251d4b125b66'),(1432,208,'flexible_1_faq_sections_0_faq_questions_and_answers_0_faq_answer','1 The lending decision is made over 15 minutes. We would need one more day to access the real estate item, to carry out all