posed terms was agreed within a few hours.\r\n\r\nThe Inflow Team worked quickly and closely with solicitors to ensure a smooth process. The client was able to complete the purchase and was saved from losing their exchange funds.'),(3131,306,'_text_content','field_625d1ef55af51'),(3132,306,'add_section_image','457'),(3133,306,'_add_section_image','field_625d1f285af52'),(3134,306,'add_section_image_s','456'),(3135,306,'_add_section_image_s','field_625d1f3a5af53'),(3136,306,'text_content_s','<h1>Key Highlights</h1>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li aria-level=\"1\">Expertise in creating bespoke lending solutions</li>\r\n 	<li aria-level=\"1\"> No survey loan</li>\r\n 	<li aria-level=\"1\"> Ultrafast turnaround to complete the loan in 2 days</li>\r\n 	<li aria-level=\"1\"> Competitive pricing in a precarious scenario</li>\r\n</ul>'),(3137,306,'_text_content_s','field_625d1f415af54'),(3138,456,'_wp_attached_file','2022/04/Single-Case-study-page-Key-Highlights-image-Inflow-Finance.png'),(3139,456,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:5:{s:5:\"width\";i:310;s:6:\"height\";i:316;s:4:\"file\";s:70:\"2022/04/Single-Case-study-page-Key-Highlights-image-Inflow-Finance.png\";s:5:\"sizes\";a:2:{s:6:\"medium\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:70:\"Single-Case-study-page-Key-Highlights-image-Inflow-Finance-294x300.png\";s:5:\"width\";i:294;s:6:\"height\";i:300;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:9:\"image/png\";}s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:70:\"Single-Case-study-page-Key-Highlights-image-Inflow-Finance-150x150.png\";s:5:\"width\";i:150;s:6:\"height\";i:150;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:9:\"image/png\";}}s:10:\"image_meta\";a:12:{s:8:\"aperture\";s:1:\"0\";s:6:\"credit\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"camera\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"caption\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"created_timestamp\";s:1:\"0\";s:9:\"copyright\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"focal_length\";s:1:\"0\";s:3:\"iso\";s:1:\"0\";s:13:\"shutter_speed\";s:1:\"0\";s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"orientation\";s:1:\"0\";s:8:\"keywords\";a:0:{}}}'),(3140,457,'_wp_attached_file','2022/04/Single-Case-study-page-Story-image-Inflow