s remaining, but there was potential to increase its value significantly once the lease had been extended.\r\n\r\nThe borrower was referred to Inflow to provide options on auction finance or bridging finance for the purchase. Inflow reviewed the scenario and was able to provide a loan facility towards the purchase and for the lease extension. The borrower refurbished the flat, extended the lease and was then able to refinance on to term lending.'),(5852,411,'_text_content','field_625d1ef55af51'),(5853,411,'add_section_image','457'),(5854,411,'_add_section_image','field_625d1f285af52'),(5855,411,'add_section_image_s','456'),(5856,411,'_add_section_image_s','field_625d1f3a5af53'),(5857,411,'text_content_s','<h1>Key Highlights</h1>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li aria-level=\"1\">First time buyer and property investor</li>\r\n 	<li aria-level=\"1\">Inflow saw the merits of the deal and facilitated a loan</li>\r\n 	<li aria-level=\"1\">Short Lease Extension funding</li>\r\n</ul>'),(5858,411,'_text_content_s','field_625d1f415af54'),(5859,411,'choose_similar_case_studies','a:3:{i:0;s:3:\"407\";i:1;s:3:\"412\";i:2;s:3:\"306\";}'),(5860,411,'_choose_similar_case_studies','field_625d41b95a5b8'),(5861,407,'add_hero_background_color',''),(5862,407,'_add_hero_background_color','field_625d2f985a5b5'),(5863,407,'hero_background_image',''),(5864,407,'_hero_background_image','field_625d2fb65a5b6'),(5865,407,'product_card_links','2'),(5866,407,'_product_card_links','field_625d146aee538'),(5867,407,'location',''),(5868,407,'_location','field_625d1894ea1da'),(5869,407,'property_type','Semi-Commercial with planning'),(5870,407,'_property_type','field_625d18a5ea1db'),(5871,407,'text_content','<h1>The Scenario</h1>\r\nA US investor with experience in the UK property market sought options on purchasing a vacant Semi-Commercial property at auction. The property had planning permission already granted for 6 additional residential units.\r\n\r\nThe borrower had Terms with a well-known lender but was let down halfway through the process to completion. As the property was an auction purchase, there was a tight deadline remaining to complete without the borrower incurring a penalty and potentially losing their deposit.\r\n\r\nInflow was able to obtain a re-type of the existing valuation and pick up the case quickly, getting familiar with the borrower and their plans and enabling completion in the timeframe. The smooth transition which Inflow undertook left a lasting impression on the borrower who has since referred us to other borrowers.'),(5872,407,'_text_content','field_625d1ef55af51'),(5873,407,'add_section_image','457'),(5874,407,'_add_section_image','field_625d1f285af52'),(5875,407,'add_section_image_s','456'),(5876,407,'_add_section_image_s','field_625d1f3a5af53'),(5877,407,'text_content_s','<h1>Key Highlights</h1>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li aria-level=\"1\">Inflow was able to adopt a loan halfway through its process to completion</li>\r\n 	<li aria-level=\"1\">Swift and knowledgeable team dealt with a foreign investor living abroad</li>\r\n 	<li aria-level=\"1\">Inflow quickly understood the loan requirements and rescued the auction purchase</li>\r\n</ul>'),(5878,407,'_text_content_s','field_625d1f415af54'),(5879,407,'choose_similar_case_studies','a:3:{i:0;s:3:\"411\";i:1;s:3:\"412\";i:2;s:3:\"410\";}'),(5880,407,'_choose_similar_case_studies','field_625d41b95a5b8'),(5881,410,'add_hero_background_color',''),(5882,410,'_add_hero_background_color','field_625d2f985a5b5'),(5883,410,'hero_background_image',''),(5884,410,'_hero_background_image','field_625d2fb65a5b6'),(5885,410,'product_card_links','2'),(5886,410,'_product_card_links','field_625d146aee538'),(5887,410,'location',''),(5888,410,'_location','field_625d1894ea1da'),(5889,410,'property_type','Vacant Semi-Commercial with potential'),(5890,410,'_property_type','field_625d18a5ea1db'),(5891,410,'text_content','<h1>The Scenario</h1>\r\nAn experienced property investor was seeking to purchase a vacant commercial property he had identified as a potential planning gain opportunity.\r\n\r\nInflow was able to provide a bridging loan at 72% LTV against the purchase and release additional funds by way of second charge loan against another property the borrower held, resulting in 100% LTV towards the purchase.'),(5892,410,'_text_content','field_625d1ef55af51'),(5893,410,'add_section_image','457'),(5894,410,'_add_section_image','field_625d1f285af52'),(5895,410,'add_section_image_s','456'),(5896,410,'_add_section_image_s','field_625d1f3a5af53'),(5897,410,'text_content_s','<h1>Key Highlights</h1>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li aria-level=\"1\">100% funding (with additional security)</li>\r\n 	<li aria-level=\"1\">Planning Gain</li>\r\n 	<li aria-level=\"1\">Development opportunity</li>\r\n 	<li aria-level=\"1\">Second Charge</li>\r\n</ul>'),(5898,410,'_text_content_s','field_625d1f415af54'),(5899,410,'choose_similar_case_studies','a:3:{i:0;s:3:\"407\";i:1;s:3:\"408\";i:2;s:3:\"303\";}'),(5900,410,'_choose_similar_case_studies','field_625d41b95a5b8'),(5901,412,'add_hero_background_color',''),(5902,412,'_add_hero_background_color','field_625d2f985a5b5'),(5903,412,'hero_background_image',''),(5904,412,'_hero_background_image','field_625d2fb65a5b6'),(5905,412,'product_card_links','1'),(5906,412,'_product_card_links','field_625d146aee538'),(5907,412,'location',''),(5908,412,'_location','field_625d1894ea1da'),(5909,412,'property_type','Freeholds, Ground Rent Portfolio'),(5910,412,'_property_type','field_625d18a5ea1db'),(5911,412,'text_content','<h1>The Scenario</h1>\r\nThe Borrowers had a large ground rent portfolio across 11 titles in London. They had existing financing from a well-established commercial lender which was due to redeem.\r\n\r\nInflow was approached to consider lending whilst a sale of the portfolio was sought. The loan required understanding of complexities of a multifaceted commercial asset class.\r\n\r\nA bespoke loan facility was provided which accommodated the borrower’s requirements. The loan was completed within 6 weeks of enquiry and enabled the borrowers to proceed with their intended projects.\r\n\r\nDue to the Global pandemic the borrowers’ exit strategy of redeeming the loan through a sale of the portfolio was delayed and they pivoted to a new strategy. Inflow took a pragmatic approach on a large complex commercial facility and provided a flexible loan extension.'),(5912,412,'_text_content','field_625d1ef55af51'),(5913,412,'add_section_image','457'),(5914,412,'_add_section_image','field_625d1f285af52'),(5915,412,'add_section_image_s','456'),(5916,412,'_add_section_image_s','field_625d1f3a5af53'),(5917,412,'text_content_s','<h1>Key Highlights</h1>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li aria-level=\"1\">Bespoke lending</li>\r\n 	<li aria-level=\"1\">Large complex commercial case completed within 6 weeks</li>\r\n 	<li aria-level=\"1\">The team at Inflow were able to identify the commercial strength of the borrowers and their portfolio, taking a pragmatic flexible view enabling swift completion</li>\r\n</ul>'),(5918,412,'_text_content_s','field_625d1f415af54'),(5919,412,'choose_similar_case_studies','a:3:{i:0;s:3:\"411\";i:1;s:3:\"306\";i:2;s:3:\"407\";}'),(5920,412,'_choose_similar_case_studies','field_625d41b95a5b8'),(5921,408,'add_hero_background_color',''),(5922,408,'_add_hero_background_color','field_625d2f985a5b5'),(5923,408,'hero_background_image',''),(5924,408,'_hero_background_image','field_625d2fb65a5b6'),(5925,408,'product_card_links','1'),(5926,408,'_product_card_links','field_625d146aee538'),(5927,408,'location',''),(5928,408,'_location','field_625d1894ea1da'),(5929,408,'property_type','Residential house'),(5930,408,'_property_type','field_625d18a5ea1db'),(5931,408,'text_content','<h1>The Scenario</h1>\r\nA TV personality sought to raise capital to enhance and build their commercial online media presence during the pandemic. Their broker approached Inflow for a Second Charge bridging loan. The borrower was bound by a Non-Disclosure Agreement with a television channel regarding their income.\r\n\r\nOur case-by-case approach to underwriting together with a practical understanding enabled Inflow to assess the merits of the case. Inflow was able to raise the required capital by working closely with the borrower and their advisors to offer an efficient and suitable solution.'),(5932,408,'_text_content','field_625d1ef55af51'),(5933,408,'add_section_image','457'),(5934,408,'_add_section_image','field_625d1f285af52'),(5935,408,'add_section_image_s','456'),(5936,408,'_add_section_image_s','field_625d1f3a5af53'),(5937,408,'text_content_s','<h1>Key Highlights</h1>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li aria-level=\"1\">Inflow was able to qualify the exit strategy via alternative approach to underwriting</li>\r\n 	<li aria-level=\"1\">Case-by-Case solution</li>\r\n 	<li aria-level=\"1\">Second Charge Loan</li>\r\n</ul>'),(5938,408,'_text_content_s','field_625d1f415af54'),(5939,408,'choose_similar_case_studies','a:3:{i:0;s:3:\"411\";i:1;s:3:\"412\";i:2;s:3:\"306\";}'),(5940,408,'_choose_similar_case_studies','field_625d41b95a5b8'),(5941,586,'flexible','a:5:{i:0;s:18:\"hero_section_large\";i:1;s:21:\"most_popular_products\";i:2;s:13:\"steps_section\";i:3;s:16:\"features_section\";i:4;s:25:\"most_popular_case_studies\";}'),(5942,586,'_flexible','field_624f096c944c5'),(5943,586,'flexible_0_main_title','Property finance for property people.'),(5944,586,'_flexible_0_main_title','field_624f0c38454d4'),(5945,586,'flexible_0_section_short_description','Fast, flexible, bespoke property finance solutions.'),(5946,586,'_flexible_0_section_short_description','field_624f0c54454d5'),(5947,586,'flexible_0_section_main_image',''),(5948,586,'_flexible_0_section_main_image','field_624f0ceb454d7'),(5949,586,'flexible_0_active','1'),(5950,586,'_flexible_0_active','field_624f09be944c8'),(5951,586,'flexible_0_button_option','a:3:{s:5:\"title\";s:32:\"Start your next property project\";s:3:\"url\";s:1:\"#\";s:6:\"target\";s:0:\"\";}'),(5952,586,'_flexible_0_button_option','field