g.</p>'),(7009,616,'_flexible_1_icon_items_sections_0_add_icon_items_row_1_add_description','field_626ba79fedb76'),(7010,616,'flexible_1_icon_items_sections_1_add_icon_items_row_0_add_icon','522'),(7011,616,'_flexible_1_icon_items_sections_1_add_icon_items_row_0_add_icon','field_626ba78cedb74'),(7012,616,'flexible_1_icon_items_sections_1_add_icon_items_row_0_add_description','<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">We keep it simple</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">One of our missions is to simplify property finance. You will speak directly to experts and decision makers, with a common-sense approach. We won’t waste your valuable time.</p>'),(7013,616,'_flexible_1_icon_items_sections_1_add_icon_items_row_0_add_description','field_626ba79fedb76'),(7014,616,'flexible_1_icon_items_sections_1_add_icon_items_row_1_add_icon','97'),(7015,616,'_flexible_1_icon_items_sections_1_add_icon_items_row_1_add_icon','field_626ba78cedb74'),(7016,616,'flexible_1_icon_items_sections_1_add_icon_items_row_1_add_description','<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">We are transparent</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Our Terms are clear, straightforward and remain unchanged throughout the process. No unpleasant surprises, changed deadlines or hidden expenses that you discover later on.</p>'),(7017,616,'_flexible_1_icon_items_sections_1_add_icon_items_row_1_add_description','field_626ba79fedb76'),(7018,616,'flexible_1_icon_items_sections_1_add_icon_items_row_2_add_icon','517'),(7019,616,'_flexible_1_icon_items_sections_1_add_icon_items_row_2_add_icon','field_626ba78cedb74'),(7020,616,'flexible_1_icon_items_sections_1_add_icon_items_row_2_add_description','<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">We aim to do more</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">We have a ‘can-do’ attitude to lending. Whether you need a refurbishment loan or a development one, our team does everything in their power to help you reach your goals.</p>'),(7021,616,'_flexible_1_icon_items_sections_1_add_icon_items_row_2_ad