et the answers to all questions you may have about short-term lending and bridging finance. Browse our frequently asked questions.'),(7678,18,'_yoast_wpseo_title','Contact Us | Inflow'),(7679,18,'_yoast_wpseo_metadesc','Have a question or need help from the Inflow team? Get in touch and we will get back to you as soon as possible.'),(7680,18,'_yoast_wpseo_estimated-reading-time-minutes',''),(7681,14,'_yoast_wpseo_title','About Us | UK Principal Lenders | Inflow'),(7682,14,'_yoast_wpseo_metadesc','Inflow is the UK\'s leading principal lender providing borrowers with fast, flexible and bespoke lending solutions.'),(7777,12,'_yoast_wpseo_title','Inflow | Property Finance for Property People'),(7778,12,'_yoast_wpseo_metadesc','The UK\'s leading specialist provider of short-term lending and bridging finance, dedicated to simplifying property finance.'),(7779,3,'_yoast_wpseo_title','Privacy Policy | Inflow'),(7780,3,'_yoast_wpseo_metadesc','Read more about our privacy policy and how we collect and use the personal information we collect on the Inflow website.'),(7781,166,'_yoast_wpseo_title','Auction Finance | Inflow'),(7782,166,'_yoast_wpseo_metadesc','Get your finances in order within tight auction time-frames. Prepare for an auction and secure the property you like.'),(7783,164,'_yoast_wpseo_title','Residential Bridging Loans | Inflow'),(7784,164,'_yoast_wpseo_metadesc','1st and 2nd charge residential bridging loans are designed for a variety of residential projects. Find out more about our criteria and terms.'),(7785,162,'_yoast_wpseo_title','Semi-Commercial and Commercial Bridging | Inflow'),(7786,162,'_yoast_wpseo_metadesc','Discover all about semi-commercial and commercial bridging created to help you gain a competitive edge in today\'s complex market.'),(7787,158,'_yoast_wpseo_title','Refurbishment Finance | Inflow'),(7788,158,'_yoast_wpseo_metadesc','Whether you are looking for light, medium or heavy refurbishment of your property project, refurbishment finance i